Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯波先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我可不希望他忽然心血来潮..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍到我们之间的战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你方阵营的情况也挺复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:30.96,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(720,720)}{\pos(992,570)}恩仇的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是那边么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也吃我几招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然想攻击姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底要折磨她到什么地步才甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你并非要针对她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想造成和我一对一的局面么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是被小瞧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高志还真是爱操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那么我就作壁上观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱敌深入 争取时间等待刃更归来么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用这种伎俩来控制西侧么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要接着上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了刃更先生和澪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我全身上下都充满了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我改变对你的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘶吼吧 白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便无法针对西侧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用局部性的攻击也能发挥白虎的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局部性啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这样如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不吸取教训啊 刃更
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想息事宁人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太贪心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会失去一切哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像五年前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀背击..你还把我当小孩看待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为不用伤人 只要展现出力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山村就会改变主意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行么 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是先代魔王的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能对性命遭到危险的女孩子坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 重要的东西只能选择一件么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能奢求更多么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你的便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是无次元..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连和精灵之间的频道都被消除了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐 对不起..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯独都不想让姐和他交手..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 剧情发展有点怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你这样就叫瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这情况应该没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更哥哥..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 刃更啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不到其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就会昏迷半天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万理亚 多亏了你让他中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能争取一些时间..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪大人 太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然操控这座大楼内所有的水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快把魔法解除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和白虎相对的是东方之青龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它翱翔天际 在空中守护大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 你觉得白虎会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说它对上空也能发挥力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕碎吧 白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高兴还太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是用了什么手段？但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚希 你疯了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助魔族之人杀无赦 哪怕是你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你的便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘了五年前的悲剧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能忘 我再也不想有那种回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 就会重蹈五年前的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这次我一定要守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我才变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护刃更想保护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话 我身为勇者就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能放任野中不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里由我来 澪大人去找刃更先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野中在这里就意味着..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他并没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚才她说了要保护刃更先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请澪大人去迎接刃更先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助亲爱的哥哥是做妹妹的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 为什么我要..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年啊 变得更像男子汉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家..对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的错 全部是我..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会..备受煎熬的并不只是我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更哥哥..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更？为什么你会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是和你起争执的时候 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我想打的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就用魔法攻击你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 野中和万理亚正在跟那个叫早濑的男人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过要阻止这场战斗只能由你来打倒白虎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐用了睡眠香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眠香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 醒一醒啊 刃更
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更啊 刃更..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把一切都..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 刃更
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 让你这么痛苦 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再稍微 再稍微加把劲吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你 这次..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次去保护万理亚和野中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我..我..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那场悲剧中 刃更也是受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们却把他逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更没有背叛我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们背叛了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..把柚希..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她帮助了魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看做敌人是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是我们的儿时玩伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是勇者一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护这个世界的使命是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你改变战斗风格了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还用这种伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负伤的人还把速度提这么高没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便现在看起来占有优势 但能撑到什么时候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当危险迫近 白虎会启动自动防御
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要防御啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于以保护使用者为己任的守护圣兽来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个命令是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高志 白虎对你来说看来还太早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡桃才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪失去了控制
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被封印的力量显现了本来的样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白虎是守护兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们不做出攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它应该就不会采取行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个结界一半是由这白虎之力构筑起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放任不管的话 结界可能会产生裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市中发生这种事的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须在一击粉碎风之障壁的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它的攻击引出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务 由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到 用这柄咲耶的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的身体太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信咱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能够为了刃更而战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这千辛万苦的五年 就是为了这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 咲耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无次元执行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是儿时玩伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前的那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀的人之中 有多少是我们的儿时玩伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 快杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个被诅咒的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕落成魔王之女的同伴的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干这种事一定很容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为被痛苦折磨的只有你们自己么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们无法忘怀的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更怎么可能忘得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪大人 冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种笨蛋 要再狠狠地揍几下才可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 放开我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还想来袭击澪 无论多少次我都会阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过去和现在的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你背负一生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情讲清楚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 你是怎么进入结界的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟控制一半结界的白虎都消失了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 事情还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务被暂时撤回了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？斯波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟高志让白虎失控的乱局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由你们动手解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在这种毫无正当性的情况下消灭她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,势必会产生污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就成了损害我们与精灵和神明间契约的大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上头也觉得担不起这个责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听到吗？高志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了事情已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也来吧 回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下 斯波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚希她..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次 只想作为监督者直至最后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再闹下去了 不然的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种威吓..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刃更 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果柚希酱她们现在不回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状况只会更加恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会变得不幸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 刃更 能再见到你很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.94,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}下回 暴走的色梦魔
